additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Beware: Deliberately sniffing or inhaling concentrated spray can be harmful or fatal. Read safety directions KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. EXTREMELY FLAMMABLE. Do not spray directly onto humans, pets, exposed food, water, food preparation areas or food utensils. May cause allergy to sensitive individuals. Do not spray near eyes or towards the face. Do not inhale spray mist. DO NOT STORE OR USE NEAR FIRE OR FLAME. DO NOT SMOKE DURING USE. Surfaces may become slippery once sprayed. Care should be taken not to spray delicate fabrics or furnishings and plastic surfaces without prior testing.
